PN,31801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FResearchers have found that looking at
OL,8,Fstructural changes to lymph nodes may
OL,9,Fhelp predict whether a person's breast
OL,10,Fcancer has a higher or lower risk of
OL,11,Fspreading.
OL,13,FA study found that the structure of a
OL,14,Fnetwork that supports lymph nodes
OL,15,Fcould change due to the disease even
OL,16,Fbefore doctors are able to spot any
OL,17,Fcancer cells in that area of the body.
OL,19,FSome changes were linked to a better
OL,20,Fchance of survival, while others led
OL,21,Fto a worse prognosis for the patient.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FResearchers said the findings could
OL,8,Fguide treatment decisions and help
OL,9,Fpeople avoid unnecessary treatment.
OL,11,FLymph nodes play a key role in the
OL,12,Fimmune system, helping the body fight
OL,13,Finfections and cancer.
OL,15,FIn breast cancer, the lymph nodes in
OL,16,Fthe armpit are often the first place
OL,17,Fthe disease spreads to and, at the
OL,18,Fmoment, everyone with invasive breast
OL,19,Fcancer undergoes surgery to remove
OL,20,Flymph nodes to check for cancer cells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FWhile this is effective, it can lead
OL,8,Fto long-term side effects like
OL,9,Fswelling of the arm (lymphoedema) and
OL,10,Fmay be unnecessary for some patients.
OL,12,FThe new research, funded by the
OL,13,Fcharity Breast Cancer Now and
OL,14,Fpublished in the Journal of Pathology,
OL,15,Faims to help identify people who are
OL,16,Fat higher or lower risk of breast
OL,17,Fcancer spreading.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FDr Simon Vincent, chief scientific
OL,8,Fofficer at Breast Cancer Now, said:
OL,9,F"These findings suggest that changes
OL,10,Fto the structure of the lymph nodes
OL,11,Fare more than just a consequence of
OL,12,Fthe cancer. They can also play an
OL,13,Factive role in helping breast cancer
OL,14,Fprogress.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"With one person tragically dying from
OL,8,Fbreast cancer every 45 minutes in the
OL,9,FUK, we urgently need research like
OL,10,Fthis so that we can better understand
OL,11,Fwho is most at risk of their cancer
OL,12,Fprogressing and becoming incurable.
OL,13,FOnly then we can find ways to stop it.
OL,15,F"With a better understanding of how
OL,16,Flymph nodes change as breast cancer
OL,17,Fspreads, we could find new targets for
OL,18,Ffuture treatments for types of breast
OL,19,Fcancer that are harder to treat."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FDr Amy Llewellyn and Dr Kalnisha
OL,8,FNaidoo from King's College London,
OL,9,Ftogether with Professor Sophie Acton
OL,10,Fat University College London, studied
OL,11,F331 lymph node samples taken from
OL,12,Fpeople with different types of breast
OL,13,Fcancer and compared them to healthy
OL,14,Flymph nodes in people free from the
OL,15,Fdisease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThey focused on a specific network of
OL,8,Fstructural cells called fibroblastic
OL,9,Freticular cells (FRC), which provides
OL,10,Fthe structure for the lymph node,
OL,11,Fcontrols fluid flow and activates
OL,12,Fdifferent immune cells.
OL,14,FThe team discovered that this FRC
OL,15,Fnetwork can change even before breast
OL,16,Fcancer has spread.
OL,18,FThese structural changes vary
OL,19,Fdepending on the type of breast cancer
OL,20,Fand whether the patient has had
OL,21,Fchemotherapy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe hope is that in the future, these
OL,8,Ffindings could support new treatments,
OL,9,Fmore tailored care and ensure more
OL,10,Fpeople avoid unnecessary side-effects.
OL,12,FDr Llewellyn said: "Until now we have
OL,13,Fnot fully understood how and when
OL,14,Flymph nodes become altered in a way
OL,15,Fthat allows cancer to spread.
OL,17,F"As a result, every breast cancer
OL,18,Fpatient currently must have some of
OL,19,Ftheir lymph nodes removed for accurate
OL,20,Fstaging and treatment planning.
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"While this is effective, it can lead
OL,8,Fto long-term complications and may be
OL,9,Funnecessary for some patients,
OL,10,Fparticularly those with early-stage
OL,11,Fdisease or those whose cancer responds
OL,12,Fwell to treatment.
OL,14,F"There is therefore an urgent need to
OL,15,Fbetter understand the biology of the
OL,16,Flymph node chain and our study
OL,17,Faddresses this gap by providing the
OL,18,Ffirst large-scale analysis of FRC in
OL,19,Fhuman lymph node tissue from breast
OL,20,Fcancer patients."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
