CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FRuth Smith, 59, from Buckinghamshire,
OL,13,Fwas diagnosed with triple negative
OL,14,Fbreast cancer in January 2023 after
OL,15,Fdiscovering a lump in her right breast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"Going through breast cancer treatment
OL,8,Fand being told that lymph nodes needed
OL,9,Fto be removed was daunting, and at the
OL,10,Ftime I just focused on doing whatever
OL,11,Fwas necessary to treat the cancer,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"Living with lymphoedema afterwards
OL,15,Fhas been a constant reminder of what I
OL,16,Fwent through ` it developed on my arm
OL,17,Flike a series of 10p pieces in April
OL,18,F2024.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780704175
OL,3,CLymph node changes can show risk of
OL,4,Cbreast cancer spreading before
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"The swelling and discomfort can have
OL,8,Fa real impact on daily life, and it's
OL,9,Fsomething I now have to manage long-
OL,10,Fterm.
OL,12,F"Research like this is so important
OL,13,Fbecause it could help doctors better
OL,14,Funderstand who really needs which
OL,15,Ftreatments, and hopefully reduce the
OL,16,Fnumber of people who go on to develop
OL,17,Flymphoedema in the future."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
